data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 4 bdrm+bonus rm, 2.5 bthrm home tucked away in the growing Spanaway community. This well maintained home comes complete w/ a lrg kitchen that leads to a deck, formal living and formal dining area. The master bdrm has a 5 piece bath & a walk in closet. Additional upgrades include a new water heater, new shower surrounds, new appls, new baseboard trim, new carpet on lower level, new paint - interior & exterior, large shed, fully fenced yard & all appliances stay.
